  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Continental is a great new addition to our Summer 2015 programme, situated in a stunning old villa built during the Austro-Hungarian period. It is well known for its house café preparing coffee in 50 different ways, the champagne bar, its delicatessen offering superb locally produced prosciutto ham, cheese and olives and the ‘Milenij Choco World’ where you will be able to experience the process of making chocolate and make your own!</p>]]></description>
